p2858
tp2859
a(I0
VWith the exhilarating romp of The Fantastic Mr. Fox (2009), all of a sudden the director found his groove\u2014by making a cartoon weirdly lifelike, rather than making life weirdly cartoon-like.
p2860
tp2861
a(I0
