p3526
tp3527
a(I1
VFrom its earworm-hole of a score (in climactic moments, Hans Zimmer\u2019s music even overwhelms the dialogue) to its warped drive through plots\u2014secret hideout-discovery, code breaking, father-daughter drama, traitor-among-us suspense, sci-fi salvation\u2014Interstellar is a bombast-and-crisis megamovie, rocket-fuelled by gobbledygeek.
p3528
tp3529
a(I0
