VBilly Wilder shows his remarkable filmmaking talents by nevertheless keeping us in suspense throughout the movie, often cited as the most impressive film noir ever made.It is such a dark script it took Wilde a while to find his cast; the characters are not very likeable and their moral compass has jammed at 'bad'.
